{"type": "article", "id": 33341, "title": "Deepmoss 带来波斯风韵时装，以及，上海衡山坊有时尚电影展映 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-15T04:26:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}, {"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 28991, "name": "Golden Goose"}, {"id": 33975, "name": "Anti Social Social Club"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161015110520WhPOAZL1Tc4X5RN0.JPG", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p>          </p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/christian-dior-maria-grazia-raf-rise-7-in-q1-10675934/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior 销售额反弹，Q1 营收上升 7%</a>&nbsp;</b>| 在 LVMH 集团本周发布的最新财报中，Dior 业绩表现良好，截止 9 月 30 日季度营收上升 7%，达 5.02 亿欧元，零售额增幅亦达 7%。此前两个季度，该品牌营收分别经历了 2.9% 和 0.9% 的下跌。上个月，Dior 新任高定女装、成衣及配饰艺术总监 Maria Grazia Chiuri 刚刚发布其上任以来的第一个成衣系列。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/government-trade/obama-lifts-some-trade-restrictions-cuba-10675758/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奥巴马进一步解除美国对古巴的贸易管制</b></a><b>&nbsp;</b>| 本周五奥巴马政府宣布将进一步解除对古巴的贸易限制。从 10 月 17 日起，美国各零售商及品牌方可直接向古巴出口服饰、鞋履及配饰等商品，无需提前申请政府许可。</p><p><b>Levi’s 母公司 Q3 恢复营收增长&nbsp;</b>| 截至 8 月 28 日的三季度，Levi’s 母公司 Levi Strauss &amp; Co. 净利润达到 9830 万美元，比去年同期增长 69%；但集团库存也从去年同期的 6069 亿美元上升至 8.512 亿美元，增幅达 40.3%。Levi Strauss &amp; Co. 总裁兼首席执行官Chip Bergh 认为批发业务依旧是集团最大业务，也是最大挑战。</p><p><b>亚马逊将招 12 万人应对假日季&nbsp;</b>| 亚马逊表示将在即将到来的假日季增加 20% 的季节性临时岗位。12 万员工将被安排在27 个州的分拣中心和客服中心。根据此前美国零售业联合会的数据，2016 年11 月和 12 月假日季销售额将增加 3.6%，其中在线零售将有7% - 10% 的增幅，至 1170 亿美元左右。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：<br></h3><p class=\"\">2017 年春夏上海时装周第三天。</p><p class=\"\">Deepmoss 带来一组波斯风韵的时装，可以看到用传统波斯头巾为灵感改造的雕塑感帽子。设计师还将石榴、建筑、器皿制作成印花图案。发布会主题取自Sergei Parajanov 于 1968 年拍摄的电影《石榴的颜色》</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101308GqXYVNM7PZK4CT1r.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500241\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101327VUA2YOzaZBWiHC36.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101335wUIGTegvAY74bWZj.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499767\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101344ga4lEVR9fYpH5Qd2.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101354FuozbneGEsTxMhDC.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500224\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101510140473cBpXvSMfVItqTF.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101415CbsJmKv3a2eA1fTM.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101425pTko7YL9cHlxI8CN.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101435pV6z4ZtmbIWiwLhx.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015101443UZPkvSCFe7d1nhlT.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499790\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Y-VISON携手女包品牌 JESSIE &amp; JANE 来了一场联名款发布，秀场的主题是”扭曲”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015100423erJPMydvmTVp8nfO.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500664\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015100457Gwo5jTJ7Cq8v3EF9.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015100505Ydoe3Vx5TIgWQLfy.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101510051347Tgzc5qvPNULQRB.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500681\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015100521XkmnFLGiSr1agRCh.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499790\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015100533sQXiLegVIEtlvh9F.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015100543eT3Caz9bLldWZvIq.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499723\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015100551CELxcnfPG0O1r3hz.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499533\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Acense 以“奇趣盛宴”为主题，展示了 2017SS 系列，使用充满质感的面料，在休闲正式当中融入趣味的小细节。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004147EJ5G3wxtuKjy8M1I.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500172\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004148Yrusn9P8RJpbNDzQ.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004235cedHLgtNAZMOlDK3.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500172\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004236pXVJHmiIBD3R4wfb.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500360\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004237k0FtUw591q6XinOv.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004237zfFNK20am3riTcRS.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004244BU5uDRLJAjmYeNlp.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610150042458N0hEy7n12dm9bxC.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004246bTiIwkr3McanJ5yO.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015004250T6QvYgsmKLeI7XPC.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500357\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>上海时装周在大时代广场前的分会场 GreenCode，倡导绿色时尚主题。值得一看的是会场里旧衣再造服装的展示。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015073835tyLHIWY3aFdGxjr4.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.539427\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015073836l7IwOxKRVc816ugk.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015073837wIdsjiFAYKNuW0PE.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">另外，ASVOFF 国际时尚影像艺术展映在在上海衡山坊举行。“ASVOFF”全名为“A SHADED VIEW ON FASHION FILM”，是由法国资深时装人 Diane Pernet 在 2008 年创办，是第一个以时装电影为主题的电影节，迄今为止已经举办了八届，而这是它第一次来中国。早年的&nbsp;ASVOFF 官网是一个时尚生活方式类的博客，现在它的赞助商有 9 个，包括国际羊毛局 (The worlmark company)。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015103014DK30os7pCcfXA9Sw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666292\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015103031mRHyrLxaSUkW3Cv5.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663697\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015103041dEVrhkelYXcfUSFz.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015103053bPWw5exQglLHvApi.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668919\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">上海时装周独立设计师展区 Labelhood 第三天，GQ 男装日在外滩源举办。共有HIUMAN、WAN HUNG、CHENPENG、STAFFONLY、 JUNWEI LIN 以及 PRONOUNCE 等 6 个独立设计师品牌展出 2017 春夏系列，其中将有一个品牌被选出参加 2018 年春夏季的伦敦时装周。</p><p class=\"\">HIUMAN 2017 SS，设计师周晓雯：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015115153Tb14fczOHXnIRrK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015115634jZE4weOPctzSFhHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015115645rK8sJvO7H5LeykYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015115740E2oyBgqmWDX6zwdQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">WAN HUNG 2017 SS，设计师张运：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015115856WCUj2omZuTKO8BAd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015115910s5HrazUvTwFDkWVK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015115919XeBWu025t36ICNLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101511592995k8Nu3bnIGjxlAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">CHENPENG 2017 SS，设计师陈鹏：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120056lMLoTZbaKp9qJAS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120109Mx8LOKlW4ru7ZUaA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120117loB4aG7AvIez51qZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101512020668cYFnhNayjCwV0Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">STAFFONLY 2017 SS，设计师温雅、周师墨：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120405LqDEtCUoaPuZA1Ir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610151204169rpwoOQJ4017d2bP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120433nEs9gSVOfyte4CbT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120450PTXw8RZUgn3eykBd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610151205029xAzwRsvIWt1M5B8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120512K8xdSjrW4l5wVkGy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562069\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">JUNWEI LIN 2017 SS，设计师林筠苇：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120706efv1UNnt08XWKiJy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120721EYTyxQIgaUiKSZhe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610151207330XhW6EYr5QIjDoAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120819j2XdNTkBqQoUcvzx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120827Vd1hSKH56Cms2ayF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015120836cao4bVwpgICNM58i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">PRONOUNCE 2017 SS，设计师周俊、李雨山：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015121023keWxZv1Jumd9NgY3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015121036D4Rzbveg2uskXV7I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015121046a3ZjKMFO7View461.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015121053fS2X3edx5RyOgQ90.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://fak3shion.com/blog/building-block-fall-2014\" rel=\"nofollow\">介绍一个来自洛杉矶的走简约风的手袋品牌&nbsp;Building Block。</a>品牌创办于 2011 年，款式有斜肩包包、背包、Clutch、Tote Bag 等。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015105156Hkcl2Z8MPdmWfKRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610151052029YTWnMGI0KLNViUw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015105210diMfPZeAWwcgvGa7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.699844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015105218f8v0wN4sEg9YkSMq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.718750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">街头品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/search?s=Anti+Social+Social+Club\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anti Social Social Club</a> 找来美国香皂公司 Aceite 推出香皂产品，味道是日本樱花。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015105725mP9jRuwQvEtp8CHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">卖“脏鞋子”的 Golden Goose 推出日本市场的限量版，包括Superstar, Francy, V-Star 和 Starter 等热门鞋型。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015105937cBPXvA903DONSdip.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666964\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015105946Lj4FK7APCEdGJrNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015105952IhrTe9kKn0W5yXcG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666062\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161015110009xYnrIEAlPuXF4UDG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}